pan class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104eva1665702625026.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eva1665702625026.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eva1665702625026.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"eva1665702625026\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"eva1665702625026__returns_237290\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define the returned data type of a function or entry. </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"eva1665702625026__topic_d76682e1_d76683e1_d76684e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eva1665702625026__p_d76685e1_d76686e1_d76687e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">returns</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DataType</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"eva1665702625026__section_w2158ab1b7b5_w2159ab1b7_w2160ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eva1665702625026__p_d76688e1_d76689e1_d76690e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">returns numeric</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eva1665702625026__topic_d50402e1_d50403e1_d50404e1_d50405e1_d50406e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d323095e77\"> Parameters </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"eva1665702625026__table_d7304e1_d7305e1_d7306e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"eva1665702625026__table_d7304e1_d7305e1_d7306e1__entry__1\"> Parameter </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"eva1665702625026__table_d7304e1_d7305e1_d7306e1__entry__2\"> Data Type </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"eva1665702625026__table_d7304e1_d7305e1_d7306e1__entry__3\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"eva1665702625026__table_d7304e1_d7305e1_d7306e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DataType</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"eva1665702625026__table_d7304e1_d7305e1_d7306e1__entry__2\"> String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"eva1665702625026__table_d7304e1_d7305e1_d7306e1__entry__3\"> A Uniface data type. For more information, see\n                           <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dld1665702530483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dld1665702530483.html\" title=\"Data types are classifications for data containers, such as fields, variables, parameters, and return values. They define the characteristics of the data and determine how the data is handled during processing and storage. Uniface has scalar data types and reference data types.\">Uniface Data Types</a>. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eva1665702625026__topic_d50407e1_d50408e1_d50409e1_d50410e1_d50411e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d323095e138\"> Return Values </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eva1665702625026__p_d76697e1_d76698e1_d76699e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">returns</span> statement does not\n            affect <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eva1665702625026__topic_d50412e1_d50413e1_d50414e1_d50415e1_d50416e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d323095e154\"> Use </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eva1665702625026__p_d76703e1_d76704e1_d76705e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eva1665702625026__p_d76706e1_d76707e1_d76708e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">returns</span> should be placed before the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">params</span>\n            block.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eva1665702625026__section_m44_vwl_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d323095e172\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">returns</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following code is an example of how to code for the ProcScript\n            statement <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">returns</span>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"eva1665702625026__pre_mlg_wwl_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">function multiply\nreturns numeric\nparams\n numeric parm1 : IN\n numeric parm2 : IN\nendparams\n\nvariables\n numeric vMultiplyResult\nendvariables\n\nvMultiplyResult = parm1 * parm2\nreturn vMultiplyResult\nend ; multiply\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ckg1665702579864.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>return</a><p>Exit from the ProcScript module, optionally returning a value to $status.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aqg1665702579072.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>entry</a><p>Declare a ProcScript entry, a script module that can be invoked from within the same component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pub1707739948228.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>operation</a><p>Declare an operation ProcScript module.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612902\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612902\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "returns Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define the returned data type of a function or entry. returns DataType Example: returns numeric Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description DataType String A Uniface data type. For more information, see Uniface Data Types . Return Values The returns statement does not affect $status . Use Allowed in all component types. returns should be placed before the params block. Example: Using returns The following code is an example of how to code for the ProcScript statement returns : function multiply returns numeric params numeric parm1 : IN numeric parm2 : IN endparams variables numeric vMultiplyResult endvariables vMultiplyResult = parm1 * parm2 return vMultiplyResult end ; multiply Copy Related Links return Exit from the ProcScript module, optionally returning a value to $status. entry Declare a ProcScript entry, a script module that can be invoked from within the same component. operation Declare an operation ProcScript module. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}